** First scenario is a list of previews
<li>
  <span>{founder}</span>
  <span>{title}</span>
  <span>{timestamp}</span>
  <span>{like/comment count}</span>
</li>

** Second scenario is a single cause in detail
<article>
  <h2>{title}</h2>
  <h3>{founder} - {datetime}</h3>
  <p>
    {actionPlan}
  </p>
  !OPTIONAL <a>{Revision History}</a>
</article>
<ul>
  ...comments
</ul>
** Final case is an editor for the cause
<main>
<label name='title'>
  <input name='title'>
  <label name='action-plan'>
  <textarea name='action-plan'>
  <aside> ***Here are tips for writing an action plan 
</main>